597.5, 849.6]}, {"text": "Insurance receivable reserve", "bbox": [75.0, 871.3, 303.3, 891.3]}, {"text": "During 2006, a Zebra reseller filed for bankruptcy protection in Austria. At the time of", "bbox": [75.0, 892.1, 757.5, 912.1]}, {"text": "the filing, the reseller owed various Zebra subsidiaries a total of $12,065,000. The entire", "bbox": [75.0, 913.0, 776.6, 932.9]}, {"text": "balance due to Zebra had been guaranteed by Condor Insurance, a Nevis-based insurance", "bbox": [75.0, 933.8, 798.3, 953.8]}, {"text": "company through a United Kingdom insurance broker. During June 2006, Zebra initiated", "bbox": [75.0, 954.6, 785.8, 974.6]}, {"text": "a suit in the U.K. courts to enforce the guarantee. However, during the fourth quarter, we", "bbox": [75.0, 975.5, 786.9, 995.4]}, {"text": "discovered that the insurance company’s financial position was such that it was unable", "bbox": [75.0, 996.3, 774.3, 1016.3]}, {"text": "to pay the judgment awarded to us. We reviewed the situation and determined that a loss", "bbox": [75.0, 1017.1, 793.7, 1037.1]}, {"text": "is probable, and, therefore, reserved 100% of the balance due, which was $12,543,000 at", "bbox": [75.0, 1038.0, 784.0, 1057.9]}, {"text": "December 31, 2006.", "bbox": [75.0, 1058.8, 236.9, 1078.8]}, {"text": "Operating Income", "bbox": [843.8, 146.7, 987.4, 166.7]}, {"text": "Operating income is summarized in the following table (in thousands, except percentages):", "bbox": [843.8, 167.5, 1551.2, 187.5]}, {"text": "Percent of", "bbox": [1466.6, 199.0, 1550.0, 217.0]}, {"text": "For the Year Ended", "bbox": [843.8, 215.6, 999.7, 233.6]}, {"text": "Operating Income", "bbox": [1225.6, 215.6, 1373.6, 233.6]}, {"text": "Net Sales", "bbox": [1474.1, 215.6, 1550.0, 233.6]}, {"text": "December 31, 2007", "bbox": [843.8, 241.3, 1001.7, 261.2]}, {"text": "$143,185", "bbox": [1299.1, 241.3, 1373.4, 261.2]}, {"text": "16.5", "bbox": [1519.2, 241.3, 1552.1, 261.2]}, {"text": "December 31, 2006", "bbox": [843.8, 262.1, 100