, 1373.4, 653.8]}, {"text": "4.2%", "bbox": [1514.6, 633.8, 1554.2, 653.8]}, {"text": "During 2007, we began liquidating all of our interests in our partnership holdings. As", "bbox": [843.8, 675.5, 1523.3, 695.4]}, {"text": "a result of these liquidations, we recorded investment income of $9,246,000 related to", "bbox": [843.8, 696.3, 1535.5, 716.3]}, {"text": "gains on the liquidations of the partnerships during 2007.", "bbox": [843.8, 717.1, 1299.9, 737.1]}, {"text": "Income Taxes", "bbox": [843.8, 758.8, 953.3, 778.8]}, {"text": "The effective income tax rate for 2007 was 34.2% versus 31.5% for 2006. The increase", "bbox": [843.8, 779.6, 1531.6, 799.6]}, {"text": "in the effective tax rate is a result of the increased impact in 2006 of permanent tax", "bbox": [843.8, 800.5, 1509.8, 820.4]}, {"text": "differences, including tax-exempt interest income, on the effective income tax rate due", "bbox": [843.8, 821.3, 1544.3, 841.3]}, {"text": "to lower taxable income as a result of the Paxar settlement. In addition, we reduced tax", "bbox": [843.8, 842.1, 1544.4, 862.1]}, {"text": "reserves in 2006 totaling $1,189,000 related to the completion of various state tax audits", "bbox": [843.8, 863.0, 1550.1, 882.9]}, {"text": "and 2005 state income tax returns.", "bbox": [843.8, 883.8, 1120.9, 903.8]}, {"text": "Income before Cumulative Effect of Accounting Change", "bbox": [843.8, 925.5, 1285.8, 945.4]}, {"text": "Zebra’s income before cumulative effect of accounting change is summarized below (in", "bbox": [843.8, 946.3, 1547.5, 966.3]}, {"text": "thousands, except per share amounts):", "bbox": [843.8, 967.1, 1156.3, 987.1]}, {"text": "Year Ended December 31,", "bbox": [1340.0, 998.5, 1544.5, 1016.6]}, {"text": "2007", "bbox": [1329.0, 1019.4, 1373.6, 1037.4]}, {"text": "2006", "bbox": [1514.1, 1019.4, 1554.2, 1037.4]}, {"text": "Income before cumulative effect", "bbox": [843.8, 1045.1, 1112.6, 1065.0]}, {"text": "of accounting change", "bbox": [843.7, 1065.9, 1034.3, 10